WEBVTT

00:02:59.999 --> 00:03:02.940
I walked into the office
and they handed me a laptop.

00:03:02.964 --> 00:03:05.424
And the laptop was running Windows 98.

00:03:05.448 --> 00:03:06.822
(Laughter)

00:03:06.846 --> 00:03:10.538
I mean, three entire presidential
elections had come and gone

00:03:10.562 --> 00:03:13.919
since the government had updated
the operating system on that computer.

00:03:13.943 --> 00:03:15.354
Three elections!

00:03:16.093 --> 00:03:17.638
Which is when we realized

00:03:17.662 --> 00:03:21.726
this problem was a whole lot bigger
than we ever could have imagined.

00:03:21.750 --> 00:03:23.506
Let me paint the picture for you.

00:03:24.290 --> 00:03:28.073
The federal government is the largest
institution in the world.

00:03:28.097 --> 00:03:32.669
It spends over 86 billion dollars
a year -- 86 billion --